00:06.673 --> 00:08.616
What is this about, Sarah?

00:08.617 --> 00:11.378
He had inappropriate... urges.

00:11.379 --> 00:16.032
What if all of this was built on
the cravings of a very sick man?

00:16.033 --> 00:17.974
I took the medicine last night.

00:17.975 --> 00:21.730
I was on one path and you
were on a different one.

00:26.849 --> 00:28.576
Best and final.

00:29.589 --> 00:32.113
